                                    <h2>Options</h2>
                                </div>
                                <div class="clearfix">
                                    <ul class="fa-ul">
                                        <li>
                                            <h3>Parameters</h3>
                                            <hr />
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <span class="label label-danger">height</span> - height of the classybox window in pixels, default is <span class="label label-primary">650</span>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <span class="label label-danger">width</span> - width of the classybox window in pixels, default is <span class="label label-primary">450</span>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <span class="label label-danger">iframe</span> - pull the contents via an iframe, can be <span class="label label-success">true</span> or <span class="label label-success">false</span>, default is <span class="label label-primary">false</span>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <span class="label label-danger">inline</span> - pull the contents inline from the DOM, can be <span class="label label-success">true</span> or <span class="label label-success">false</span>, default is <span class="label label-primary">false</span>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <span class="label label-danger">ajax</span> - pull the contents via an AJAX request, can be <span class="label label-success">true</span> or <span class="label label-success">false</span>, default is <span class="label label-primary">false</span>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <span class="label label-danger">social</span> - should the plugin display social media links, can be <span class="label label-success">true</span> or <span class="label label-success">false</span>, default is <span class="label label-primary">true</span>
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
